## 🚀 Getting Started

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/TimeGauge.git
cd TimeGauge
```

Open `index.html` in your browser, or enable GitHub Pages for the repository to use the hosted version.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (ES Modules)
* Local Storage API
* Web Audio API

No backend or external frameworks are required.

